ComicInfo.Summary: Sonja tracks down the thieves who have stolen treasure from Lady Rosenda but finds that they are a trio of sisters who have a tale of woe to tell. The Emoran empire has taken over their land of Sogaria and they have resorted to stealing to support themselves. Sonja is traveling with the girls to recover the lost treasure when they are ambushed by Emorans. They are taken to a massive Emoran slave camp where Sonja quickly dispatches their captors and vows to put an end to this detestable enterprise.
